    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "The Hawaiian Airlines Boeing 767: A new era in transpacific flight begins.\nHAWAIIAN",
      "HAWAIIAN\n- AIRLINES.\nWINGS of the ISLANDS\nHawaiian Airlines is upgrading its entire transpacific\nfleet to the world's most popular twin-aisle, widebody\njets: the Boeing 767-300ER. On O'ahu, call 838-1555.\nNeighbor Islands: 800-882-8811. U.S. Mainland: 800-\n367-5320. Surf's up at hawaiianair.com\n2015.166.0747"
    ],
